Package: TDMM
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Time-Dynamic Mixed-Effects Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Makena", "Grigsby", email = "makenavgrigsby@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Esra", "Kurum", role = "aut")
    )
 Description: Fits Bayesian time-dynamic mixed-effects models for longitudinal
    data with baseline covariates. The package supports Gaussian, Bernoulli,
    and Poisson outcomes using spline-based time-varying coefficient functions
    and subject-specific random intercepts. Posterior computation is performed
    using JAGS.
